
The TeraGrid CSA SAGA installation
----------------------------------


  In order to use this installation of SAGA (version '1.5.3'), you
  need to set the following environment variables:



  C++:
  
    Settings for C++ bindings
  
      export SAGA_LOCATION=/share1/projects/tg/SAGA/saga/1.5.3/gcc-4.1.2/
      export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=:/share1/projects/tg/SAGA/external/python/2.7.1/gcc-4.1.2//lib/:/share1/projects/tg/SAGA/external/boost/1.44.0/gcc-4.1.2//lib/::/share1/projects/tg/SAGA/external/postgresql/9.0.2/gcc-4.1.2//lib/::/share1/projects/tg/SAGA/external/sqlite3/3.6.13/gcc-4.1.2//lib/::/share1/projects/tg/SAGA/saga/1.5.3/gcc-4.1.2//lib/:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH



  Python:

    Please use /share1/projects/tg/SAGA/external/python/2.7.1/gcc-4.1.2//bin/python as python interpreter.
    BigJob is installed in /share1/projects/tg/SAGA/saga/1.5.3/gcc-4.1.2/lib/python2.7.1/site-packages//bigjob .

    Settings for Python bindings

      export PYTHONPATH=/share1/projects/tg/SAGA/saga/1.5.3/gcc-4.1.2/lib/python2.7.1/site-packages/:/share1/projects/tg/SAGA/external/python/2.7.1/gcc-4.1.2//lib/python2.7/site-packages/:$PYTHONPATH




